@startuml
title Auth Client Request Inference and Typing (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
skinparam noteBorderColor #000000

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #BBDEFB
component "auth.request(...)\nmethod inference strategy" as RequestSurface #B2DFDB
component "Inference Rules\n1 explicit method wins\n2 body => POST\n3 endpoint-aware defaults" as InferenceRules #FFF59D
component "Endpoint-aware GET set\n(get-session/list/verify/etc.)" as EndpointGetSet #C5E1A5
component "Shared auth types\nAthenaAuthUser + AthenaAuthLinkedAccount" as SharedTypes #D1C4E9

Consumer --> RequestSurface : request({ endpoint, body?, query? })
RequestSurface --> InferenceRules : safe defaults
InferenceRules --> EndpointGetSet : avoid accidental GET/POST mismatch
RequestSurface --> SharedTypes : reuse instead of inline ad hoc types

note right of InferenceRules
Known POST endpoints with empty payload now
default to POST without requiring caller hints.
Dynamic reset-password token route still defaults GET.
end note
@enduml
